                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7064" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0171</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7853 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华润集团的社会责任：用“希望”之火点亮扶贫之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Social Responsibility of China Resources Holdings: Lighting the Road to Poverty Alleviation with the Fire of “Hope”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">魏明，赵青，籍盈盈，童焱琪</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安邮电大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华润（集团）有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华润集团；希望小镇；脱贫攻坚；战略性企业社会责任</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">China Resources Holdings；Hope Town；Poverty alleviation；Strategic Corporate Social Responsibility</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“十二年，十二座。”这是华润集团建设希望小镇的扶贫之路、参与乡村振兴的一个缩影。华润集团作为红色央企，在多个革命老区、贫困乡村建立华润希望小镇，积极践行社会责任，承担起脱贫攻坚的重任。本案例以华润集团建设红安华润希望小镇为例，描述华润集团依据其多元化发展的战略目标，选择通过建设希望小镇来履行社会责任。在建设希望小镇扶贫过程中，对红安县的第一二三产业进行了融合，形成了富有特色的“田园综合体”智慧农庄，向我们展现了华润集团建设红安希望小镇所做出的贡献，同时实现了小镇与集团在经济上的合作共赢。华润集团积极践行社会责任，不仅树立了切实履行社会责任的良好企业形象，也能为其他企业产业扶贫提供借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">“Twelve China Resources Hope Towns were established in twelve years.”This is a microcosm of China Resources Holdings’ road to poverty alleviation and participation in rural revitalization in building Hope Town. As a red state-owned enterprise, China Resources Holdings has established China Resources Hope Towns in many old revolutionary bases and impoverished villages, actively fulfilling its social responsibilities, and taking on the important task of poverty alleviation. 
This case takes the construction of Hong’an China Resources Hope Town by China Resources Holdings as an example, and describes that China Resources Holdings has chosen to fulfill its social responsibility by constructing the Hope Town according to its strategic goal of diversified development. During the process of poverty alleviation in the construction of the Hope Town, the first, second and third industries of Hong’an County are integrated, forming a characteristic “pastoral complex” smart farm, which demonstrates to us the contribution made by China Resources Holdings in the construction of Hong’an Hope Town, and at the same time realizes the win-win economic cooperation between the town and the Group. China Resources Holdings has actively fulfilled its social responsibility, not only establishing a good corporate image to fulfill its social responsibility, but also providing reference for other enterprises in poverty alleviation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业商业伦理》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业社会责任理论；产业融合理论；战略性企业社会责任理论；利益相关者理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-02</td>
                            </tr>
